</div>
<div type="commentary">
<head>Commentary</head>
<p>The cult was probably initiated in or soon after 39 B.C., when the Romands gave the city eleutheria (<xref type="inscription" n="508" href="080027">8.27</xref>); there is a strong probability that the priest for life named here was C. Julius Zoilos. See most recently <bibl n="jmr1996b">Reynolds, 'Ruler-cult' 43</bibl>.</p>
</div>
